<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="at-all-costs-at-any-cost">at all costs / at any cost</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>不惜任何代价：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I decided to try at all costs to rid my students of their fear and dislike of books. 
我决定不惜一切代价尽力使学生们摆脱对书籍的恐惧和反感。</p><footer>2015 浙江改</footer></div></div>